    "Similarly, the schemes of Ghali et al. (2014c) and Kim et al. (2015), Kim et al. (2017) fall under average verification overhead.",
    "Ghali et al. (2014c) improve their own scheme Ghali et al. (2014b) by presenting a Ranking Algorithm (RA) that eliminates the Extra Overhead problem by verifying the cache hit contents only.",
    "Likewise, Kim et al. (2015), Kim et al. (2017) minimizes the verification overhead on the router unlike Ahmed et al. (2017); Yi et al. (2013); Li et al. (2018).",
    "The authors store and verify only the cache hit contents in CS which reduces the high overhead of verification.",
    "In comparison, the high and average overheads, the schemes of Hu et al. (2018) Li et al. (2014, 2017), and Ribeiro et al. (2016) stand out on low verification overhead, suggesting that the given scheme can minimize the usage of the network resources."
